{
  "texts": [
    "b) The use and sharing of healthcare data are also limited by ethics [382].",
    "Healthcare contains a lot of private information from the human body which is sensitive and risky, like genes.",
    "The use and sharing of these data are strictly restricted by laws and data owners.",
    "Once it is collected on a large scale in the absence of governance and used for the training of foundation models, it will be dangerous.",
    "In the further application of HFMs, the uncontrollable external environment also will enlarge this risk."
  ]
}